translations: n.小雌马，小母马（通常未满四岁）；活泼的小姑娘

phrs.translation: 雌马驹, 小雌马, 小姑娘, 小母马
挽用后备母马, 挽用育成母马

sentences.sentence: I want to name a baby filly PS I Love You.
sentences.translation: 我想要个孩子的名字菲伊聚苯乙烯我爱你。

sentences.sentence: The filly has been raced twice this season.
sentences.translation: 这匹小母马本季度曾两次参赛。

sentences.sentence: Expert comment: This little filly will be the star in the short, symmetrical shape.
sentences.translation: 专家点评：此小雌马将会是中短途之星，体形匀称。
